{"tid":1913600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用支那話講一次：疫帶疫路 輸出病毒","createTime":"2020-03-07T02:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T03:14:28.000Z","uid":26876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"03f5aa6caa33314ea56b59ce0c6ba9547e1ceb04","tid":1913600,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:38:19.000Z","msg":"用支那話講比支那人知"},{"pid":"dffc23af3e1e97d871d4c78f22bbc82b42ea896b","tid":1913600,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"曱甴強<br />\n習曱甴"},{"pid":"573d51909525a3c6f99248899ac008d304bfeafb","tid":1913600,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T02:58:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99ab2312d8fc94545778750c87a4f2930c8965c0","tid":1913600,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:04:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e77be316f11768bb21d64e4140572c79b25c63c","tid":1913600,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:14:28.000Z","msg":"推，推到全球知曉<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}